ething simpler or more specific to their use case.\n\nThe most likely scenario is they want a decorator around `IFileSystem` that adds cross-cutting concerns like logging, error handling, or path normalization. I should ask what specific functionality they need the wrapper to provide.","outputTokens":560,"requestId":"A039:10A559:1B24ACF:1ECECFF:69FE9585"},"id":"714ef71b-c8cd-4b7b-a6e7-8e3ef0b7d79b","timestamp":"2026-05-09T02:01:53.479Z","parentId":"d1143a74-8a0a-4b21-9959-1500a7189776"}
